	<a href="http://www.agnula.org/documentation/">The AGNULA project - AGNULA Documentation</a>.&nbsp; After reading the top-level tutorial documentation, I came back to the overall page to see what kind of license is being employed for the documentation that is being created to hold this compilation project together.&nbsp; I can't find a documentation license.&nbsp; My, my.<br /><br />I am definitely coming up with a case of bad attitude around this effort.&nbsp; And I really like the work that is being done in Italy on various open-source technologies.&nbsp; I think I will go perform some kind of penance in my own space.<br>
