	<a href="http://www.advogato.org/trust-metric.html">Advogato's trust metric</a>.&nbsp; Advogato is also an experiment in application of a trust metric.&nbsp; My eyes glaze over looking at the particular approach, although I do recall when this work was begun.&nbsp; It could work as a device for creating trust networks in accidental communities that have some requirement for trust appraisal and, perhaps, some consequences-diminishing maneuvers.&nbsp; For my work, this is interesting with regard to bootstrapping of communities and working through trust considerations that influence agreements to participate in distributed operation and also have a ductile response against a rapidly-spread corrupted object.<br /><br />Getting back to the social aspects, I am not sure I have any reason going farther than just this much.<br>
